See ?tryCatch.

Example: Function returning NULL if cancelled:

fileChoose <- function(...) {
  pathname <- NULL;
  tryCatch({
    pathname <- file.choose();
  }, error = function(ex) {
  })
  pathname;
}

/Henrik

